DERIVATIVE WORK NOTICE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The pre-patched files under overrides/prepatched/ are modified versions
of backend/handler/filesystem/roms_handler.py from the RomM project:

  https://github.com/rommapp/romm
  Copyright (C) the RomM contributors
  Licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0

Modifications made in this project add a C extension fast path
(see src/_fasthash.c) for GIL-released parallel hashing, with full
fallback to the original Python implementation when the extension is
unavailable.

